   "source": [
    "## Tuple\n",
    "#Given an integer,n, and space-separated integers as input, create a tuple,t, of those integers. Then compute and print the result of tuple."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "c3b19177-73e2-4d55-835b-bbb7d20ae5d4",
   "metadata": {},
